      <div class="sub-panel" id="sub-handbook">
        <div class="section-header"><h3>Employee Handbook</h3><div class="divider"></div></div>
        <div class="handbook-progress"><div class="progress-bar-wrap"><div class="progress-label">Handbook Completion</div><div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress-fill" id="progress-fill" style="width:0%"></div></div></div><div class="progress-count"><span id="progress-num">0</span>/5</div></div>
        <div class="complete-badge" id="handbook-complete"><h3>✅ Handbook Complete!</h3><p>All required sections initialed. Acknowledgments sent to payroll.</p></div>
        <div class="handbook-chapter"><div class="chapter-header" onclick="toggleChapter(this)"><div class="chapter-num" id="num-1">1</div><div class="chapter-title-wrap"><div class="chapter-title">About This Manual &amp; Company Overview</div><div class="chapter-type read-only">📘 Read — No initials required</div></div><span class="chapter-arrow">▼</span></div><div class="chapter-body"><div class="chapter-content"><p>While Bella Terra was established as, and is registered as, a limited liability corporation, we use the terms "Bella Terra, LLC," "Bella Terra," and "the Company" interchangeably throughout this manual.</p><p style="margin-top:0.75rem">Employees are encouraged to ask questions and provide feedback to their Team Leader, Foreman, Supervisor, or Management. Please bring any errors or suggestions to the attention of Heather Hooper.</p><h4>Purpose</h4><p>This manual is designed to develop clear communication of company policies and provide a positive contribution to team morale and operational success.</p></div></div></div>
        <div class="handbook-chapter"><div class="chapter-header" onclick="toggleChapter(this)"><div class="chapter-num" id="num-2">2</div><div class="chapter-title-wrap"><div class="chapter-title">New Employee Onboarding &amp; Required Forms</div><div class="chapter-type initial" id="type-2">✍ Initial required after reading</div></div><span class="chapter-arrow">▼</span></div><div class="chapter-body"><div class="chapter-content"><h4>Pre-Hire Screening</h4><p>All potential employees are subject to pre-employment drug and alcohol testing.</p><h4>Required Forms Upon Hire</h4><ul><li><strong>USCIS Form I-9</strong> — Identity and employment authorization</li><li><strong>W-4</strong> — Federal tax withholding</li><li><strong>Direct Deposit Form</strong></li><li><strong>Trade Secret &amp; Non-Solicitation Agreement</strong></li><li><strong>4/10 Work Agreement</strong> (signed annually)</li><li><strong>Breaks &amp; Meal Period Acknowledgment</strong> (signed annually)</li></ul></div><div class="initial-block"><p><strong>Initial to confirm:</strong> I have read and understand the New Employee Onboarding section.</p><div class="initial-row"><input type="text" placeholder="Initials" id="init-2" maxlength="4"><button class="btn-initial" onclick="saveInitial(2)">Confirm Initials</button><div class="initial-done" id="done-2">✅ Initialed</div></div></div></div></div>
        <div class="handbook-chapter"><div class="chapter-header" onclick="toggleChapter(this)"><div class="chapter-num" id="num-3">3</div><div class="chapter-title-wrap"><div class="chapter-title">Operations, Scheduling &amp; Payroll</div><div class="chapter-type initial" id="type-3">✍ Initial required after reading</div></div><span class="chapter-arrow">▼</span></div><div class="chapter-body"><div class="chapter-content"><h4>4/10 Work Week</h4><p>Bella Terra operates on a 4/10 schedule — four 10-hour days per week.</p><h4>Rest and Meal Breaks</h4><ul><li>Paid 10-minute rest break for every 4 hours worked</li><li>Unpaid 30-minute meal break when working more than 5 hours</li><li>Breaks may not be skipped or waived to leave early</li></ul><h4>Payroll</h4><ul><li>Time cards must be accurately completed each day</li><li>Overtime is calculated on hours worked over 40 per week</li><li>Direct deposit is available and encouraged</li></ul></div><div class="initial-block"><p><strong>Initial to confirm:</strong> I have read and understand Bella Terra's scheduling, break, and payroll policies.</p><div class="initial-row"><input type="text" placeholder="Initials" id="init-3" maxlength="4"><button class="btn-initial" onclick="saveInitial(3)">Confirm Initials</button><div class="initial-done" id="done-3">✅ Initialed</div></div></div></div></div>
        <div class="handbook-chapter"><div class="chapter-header" onclick="toggleChapter(this)"><div class="chapter-num" id="num-4">4</div><div class="chapter-title-wrap"><div class="chapter-title">Employee Health &amp; Welfare / Paid Sick Leave</div><div class="chapter-type read-only">📘 Read — No initials required</div></div><span class="chapter-arrow">▼</span></div><div class="chapter-body"><div class="chapter-content"><h4>Paid Sick Leave</h4><p>Employees earn 1 hour of paid sick leave for every 40 hours worked.</p><h4>Employer-Funded Medical Care</h4><p>Bella Terra covers up to 4 visits per year at <strong>Vital Care Primary &amp; Urgent Care</strong>, 1207 SE Rasmussen Blvd, Suite 119, Battle Ground, WA · (360) 723-0528</p></div></div></div>
        <div class="handbook-chapter"><div class="chapter-header" onclick="toggleChapter(this)"><div class="chapter-num" id="num-5">5</div><div class="chapter-title-wrap"><div class="chapter-title">Drug &amp; Alcohol Policy</div><div class="chapter-type initial" id="type-5">✍ Initial required after reading</div></div><span class="chapter-arrow">▼</span></div><div class="chapter-body"><div class="chapter-content"><h4>Zero Tolerance Policy</h4><p>Bella Terra has a zero-tolerance policy for illegal substances and alcohol use during work hours.</p><h4>Marijuana — Washington State Notice</h4><p><strong>Any detectable level of marijuana impairment during work hours is prohibited.</strong></p></div><div class="initial-block"><p><strong>Initial to confirm:</strong> I have read and understand Bella Terra's Drug &amp; Alcohol Policy.</p><div class="initial-row"><input type="text" placeholder="Initials" id="init-5" maxlength="4"><button class="btn-initial" onclick="saveInitial(5)">Confirm Initials</button><div class="initial-done" id="done-5">✅ Initialed</div></div></div></div></div>
        <div class="handbook-chapter"><div class="chapter-header" onclick="toggleChapter(this)"><div class="chapter-num" id="num-6">6</div><div class="chapter-title-wrap"><div class="chapter-title">Out-of-Town Project Housing Policy</div><div class="chapter-type initial" id="type-6">✍ Initial required after reading</div></div><span class="chapter-arrow">▼</span></div><div class="chapter-body"><div class="chapter-content"><h4>Strictly Prohibited in Company Housing</h4><ul><li>Alcohol in any form</li><li>Illegal drugs or marijuana</li><li>Vaping or tobacco products indoors</li><li>Guests not employed by Bella Terra on the same project</li></ul><h4>Room Assignments &amp; Privacy</h4><p><strong>Any employee sharing housing with employees of a different gender will be assigned a private bedroom with a private or en-suite bathroom.</strong></p></div><div class="initial-block"><p><strong>Initial to confirm:</strong> I have read and understand Bella Terra's Housing Policy.</p><div class="initial-row"><input type="text" placeholder="Initials" id="init-6" maxlength="4"><button class="btn-initial" onclick="saveInitial(6)">Confirm Initials</button><div class="initial-done" id="done-6">✅ Initialed</div></div></div></div></div>
        <div class="handbook-chapter"><div class="chapter-header" onclick="toggleChapter(this)"><div class="chapter-num" id="num-7">7</div><div class="chapter-title-wrap"><div class="chapter-title">Trade Secret &amp; Non-Solicitation Agreement</div><div class="chapter-type initial" id="type-7">✍ Initial required after reading</div></div><span class="chapter-arrow">▼</span></div><div class="chapter-body"><div class="chapter-content"><h4>Protected Confidential Information</h4><ul><li>Hydroseeding application techniques, seed mixes, mulch formulas</li><li>Customer lists, contact information, pricing, and project history</li><li>Equipment settings, operational procedures, and efficiency methods</li></ul><h4>Non-Solicitation of Customers</h4><p>For <strong>18 months following separation</strong> from Bella Terra, you agree not to directly solicit any current Bella Terra customer.</p></div><div class="initial-block"><p><strong>Initial to confirm:</strong> I have read and agree to Bella Terra's Trade Secret &amp; Non-Solicitation policy.</p><div class="initial-row"><input type="text" placeholder="Initials" id="init-7" maxlength="4"><button class="btn-initial" onclick="saveInitial(7)">Confirm Initials</button><div class="initial-done" id="done-7">✅ Initialed</div></div></div></div></div>
        <div id="handbook-submit-wrap" style="display:none;margin-top:1.5rem;"><div class="sig-card"><h4>Submit Handbook Acknowledgment</h4><div class="description">All required sections initialed. Submit to send your acknowledgment to payroll.</div><div class="form-row"><div class="form-group"><label>Full Name</label><input type="text" id="hb-name" placeholder="First Last"></div><div class="form-group"><label>Date</label><input type="date" id="hb-date"></div></div><button class="btn-submit" onclick="submitHandbook()">📤 Submit Acknowledgment</button><div class="success-msg" id="hb-success">✅ Acknowledgment sent to payroll</div></div></div>
