        <div class="sig-card"><h4>📅 4/10 Work Schedule Agreement</h4><div class="description">Must be signed at the beginning of each calendar year or upon first login on a new device.</div><div class="doc-preview"><h5>Bella Terra LLC — 4/10 Work Schedule Agreement</h5><p>I understand and agree to Bella Terra's 4/10 work schedule — four (4) ten (10) hour workdays per week. I understand that:</p><ul><li>My standard workday will be 10 hours, not including unpaid meal breaks</li><li>Overtime is calculated on hours in excess of 40 per workweek</li><li>My specific days and hours will be assigned by my supervisor and may vary seasonally</li><li>This agreement is reviewed and re-executed annually</li></ul></div><div class="form-row"><div class="form-group"><label>Full Name</label><input type="text" id="410-name" placeholder="First Last"></div><div class="form-group"><label>Position</label><input type="text" id="410-position" placeholder="e.g. Hydroseeder Operator"></div></div><div class="form-row"><div class="form-group"><label>Date of Hire</label><input type="date" id="410-hire"></div><div class="form-group"><label>Today's Date</label><input type="date" id="410-date"></div></div><div class="sig-pad-wrap"><label>Employee Signature (draw below)</label><canvas class="sig-pad" id="canvas-410" width="500" height="120"></canvas><div class="sig-controls"><button class="btn-clear" onclick="clearSig('canvas-410')">✕ Clear</button><span style="font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--gray-mid);align-self:center">Draw with mouse or finger</span></div></div><div class="consent-check"><input type="checkbox" id="consent-410"><label for="consent-410">By checking this box and signing above, I acknowledge this constitutes my electronic signature and I agree to the 4/10 Work Schedule Agreement.</label></div><button class="btn-submit" onclick="submitForm('410')">📤 Submit Agreement</button><div class="success-msg" id="success-410">✅ 4/10 Agreement submitted to payroll</div></div>
        <div class="sig-card"><h4>🍽 Break &amp; Meal Period Acknowledgment</h4><div class="description">Washington State requires annual documentation that employees understand rest and meal break rights.</div><div class="doc-preview"><h5>Bella Terra — Break &amp; Meal Period Acknowledgment</h5><p><strong>Rest Breaks (Paid):</strong> 10 minutes for every 4 hours worked. Cannot be waived to leave early.</p><p style="margin-top:0.5rem"><strong>Meal Breaks (Unpaid):</strong> 30 minutes when working more than 5 hours.</p><ul style="margin-top:0.5rem"><li>Take your assigned breaks as scheduled</li><li>Immediately notify your supervisor if you cannot take a break</li></ul></div><div class="form-row"><div class="form-group"><label>Full Name</label><input type="text" id="breaks-name" placeholder="First Last"></div><div class="form-group"><label>Position</label><input type="text" id="breaks-position" placeholder="e.g. Crew Member"></div></div><div class="form-row"><div class="form-group"><label>Date of Hire</label><input type="date" id="breaks-hire"></div><div class="form-group"><label>Today's Date</label><input type="date" id="breaks-date"></div></div><div class="sig-pad-wrap"><label>Employee Signature (draw below)</label><canvas class="sig-pad" id="canvas-breaks" width="500" height="120"></canvas><div class="sig-controls"><button class="btn-clear" onclick="clearSig('canvas-breaks')">✕ Clear</button><span style="font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--gray-mid);align-self:center">Draw with mouse or finger</span></div></div><div class="consent-check"><input type="checkbox" id="consent-breaks"><label for="consent-breaks">By checking this box and signing above, I acknowledge this constitutes my electronic signature and I agree to Bella Terra's Break &amp; Meal Period policies.</label></div><button class="btn-submit" onclick="submitForm('breaks')">📤 Submit Acknowledgment</button><div class="success-msg" id="success-breaks">✅ Acknowledgment submitted to payroll</div></div>
